'''Javriel''' was a citizen of the [[Outbound Flight Colony]]. In [[20 ABY/Legends|20 ABY]], Javriel went insane and attempted to take the colony's nursery hostage. [[Evlyn Tabory]] aided her uncle [[Guardian of the People|Guardian]] [[Jorad Pressor]] in diffusing the situation.

